So the way we'll do that is we'll add a new layer will come down to our island will select its shape

00:01:57.650 --> 00:02:06.120
then we can close that back up then we're going to select this blue here and then using our brush tool

00:02:06.120 --> 00:02:09.300
with a soft edge.

