00:02:18.570 --> 00:02:26.310
go a little bit higher like so then we're going to select our water shape and we're going to delete

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:30.700
out the area that's underneath the water.

00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:39.180
Now we're going to put our layer on lighten so and it will bring down the opacity.

00:02:39.180 --> 00:02:43.610
Now we'll do the same thing for this island and we're just going to keep it on the same layer.

